Huggpunkt VHS is undergoing a complete rewrite. The rewritten
code, which will be released as version 0.4.0 once the basic
functionality is completed, is contained within this repository.

For build instructions, please refer to the following url:

    https://github.com/simio/H.VHS/wiki/Build-environment

Development has stalled due to lack of time, and will be continued
no sooner than 2015. Another program which solves the same
problem, though with a narrower scope, is being actively developed
and maintained at:

    https://github.com/simio/teve
